| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4048 — Recovery Inhibition (securotrop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6afb3ce3-d298-53e2-8955-7ed72ddcd89c"
